summary: AN ORDINANCE transferring partial jurisdiction over certain City (Department of Parks and Recreation) real property in the Northwest quarter of Section 15, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W.M. to the Engineering Department for construction, reconstruction, and maintenance of a seawall with appurtenances, in conjunction with the Beach Drive Southwest Seawall, 3300-3500 Blocks, project (R/W 8766).
